<item>
            <title>[FELIX-387] Fix support for reference service target properties</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-387</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently Felix SCR does not reflect the service reference target settings in the component properties and on the other hand setting such target properties has no influence on the service dependencies.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Reference target properties are defined in Section 112.6, Component Properties, with respect to reflect the reference target setting as properties and 112.7, Deployment, with respect to overwriting the reference target with configuration.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
