                            <comment id="12531771" author="fmeschbe" created="Tue, 2 Oct 2007 12:36:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Adding a service after initial component activation does not work as services matching the target filter (if none is set all filters match implicitly) are ignored instead of being handled&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
